# Leftover from the old notary-server era (ECDSA P-256 signing key). The new
# verifier-server does not need a long-lived signing key, so these patterns are
# kept purely defensively: if anyone accidentally drops a `.key` or `.pem` into
# this repo during testing, git won't pick it up.
keys/
*.key
*.pem

# Local build artifacts (only relevant if you `docker build` here)
target/
